messages.message:
Hi team this use case is Bordeaux ingestion, best described in here https://docs.google.com/file/d/1Nip8V6uxB-Xd1l8BmV4ll2OKeU4k3aON/edit?usp=docslist_api&filetype=mspresentation (https://docs.google.com/file/d/1Nip8V6uxB-Xd1l8BmV4ll2OKeU4k3aON/edit?usp=docslist_api&filetype=mspresentation)

But in short lots of different excel formats with broadly the same data points but different column headers. We need to take the columns of data, apply business rules against each one and provide a single excel output in their desired format per set of Bordeaux documents.
